.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/marry-me-chickpeas-3-1x1.jpg 1w, https://www.liveeatlearn.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/marry-me-chickpeas-3-150x100.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
