<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-serving-suggestions">Serving Suggestions</h2>


<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>With vegetables</strong>, like these <a href="https://www.liveeatlearn.com/how-to-air-fry-any-vegetable/">air fryer veggies</a> which can cook while the chickpeas cook</li>



<li><strong>With bread</strong>, like crusty sourdough, fluffy naan, or toasted rye</li>



<li><strong>With rice</strong>, like jasmine or basmati rice</li>
</ul>


