an style="color: var(--wp--preset--color--foreground)"> | </span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-container wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-container-calcium"><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-label  wprm-block-text-normal" style="color: var(--wp--preset--color--foreground)">Calcium: </span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-value" style="color: #333333">215</span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-unit" style="color: #333333">mg</span></span><span style="color: var(--wp--preset--color--foreground)"> | </span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-container wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-container-iron"><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-label  wprm-block-text-normal" style="color: var(--wp--preset--color--foreground)">Iron: </span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-value" style="color: #333333">3</span><span class="wprm-nutrition-label-text-nutrition-unit" style="color: #333333">mg</span></span></div></div><p class="has-small-font-size">Nutrition information calculated by Sarah Bond, degreed nutritionist.</p></div>
