				<div class="comment-metadata">
					<time datetime="2026-01-11T21:16:16-07:00">January 11, 2026 at 9:16 pm</time>				</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

							</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://www.liveeatlearn.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" /><br />
Amazing! Added a full bag of spinach with the cream and Parm! Delicious</p>
			</div><!-- .comment-content -->

